[26/03/2019 10:52:31] <font color="#ffffff">Un Fab Lab es un laboratorio</font>
[26/03/2019 10:52:31] <font color="#ffffff">de fabricación digital</font>
[26/03/2019 10:52:33] <font color="#ffffff">o "fabrication laboratory"</font>
